HEADWORD: Lambative
<hw>Lam"ba*tive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A medicine taken by licking
with the tongue; a lincture.</def> <rj><au>Wiseman.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

